author: Danny Schwartz
title: Drake, Lil Wayne, Desiigner Were Answers On "Jeopardy!" Last Night
text:
Home > Music > Drake, Lil Wayne, Desiigner Were Answers On "Jeopardy!" Last Night Drake, Lil Wayne, Desiigner Were Answers On "Jeopardy!" Last Night 0 0 Posted by Danny Schwartz , Feb 21, 2017 at 10:37am Watch Alex Trebek spit some of the hottest bars you've ever seen. 
Last night's episode of 'Jeopardy!' featured a category called “Let’s Rap, Kids!” Meaning that Alex Trebek had the opportunity to rap lyrics from five well-known songs: Drake ’s “Started From the Bottom,” Kendrick Lamar ’s “m.A.A.d. city,” Lil Wayne ’s “6 Foot 7 Foot,” Desiigner ’s “Panda” and Kanye West ’s “Famous.” 
“I was just getting into this rap thing, I’m not too good at it, but I was getting in to it," Trebek joked after the reading the last clue. 
Watch Trebek spitting them flames below.
